name: PFP Hunters
description: The rapid increase in the demand of animal PFPs have unfortunately led to an increase in the popularity of the illegal animal trade.  Young professionals, disappointed with the low compensation in the current job market, have now changed career paths, risking their life and safety in search of tracking down and claiming only the rarest, most elusive, and dangerous of animals.  A successful hunt and kill is the greatest badge of honor.  A rare head, mounted as a trophy, for all to see. At least until its sale to the highest bidder.
